<div class="page-header">
  <h1>Brand Personality</h1>
  <p class="lead">{{ '"Better than human."' }} Codified brand traits for consistent expression across all touchpoints.</p>
</div>

<section class="section" id="brand-essence">
  <h2>Brand Essence</h2>

  <div class="essence-grid">
    <div class="essence-card featured">
      <span class="label">Tagline</span>
      <h3>Better than human.</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="essence-card">
      <span class="label">Promise</span>
      <p>Finally, someone who actually listens.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="essence-card">
      <span class="label">Mission</span>
      <p>We believe in making AI human, and the decisions we make will reflect that.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="essence-card">
      <span class="label">Position</span>
      <p>The AI that actually listens - filling the gaps when your people aren't available.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section" id="core-traits">
  <h2>Core Traits</h2>
  <p>The 5 core personality traits that define Ferni across all touchpoints.</p>

  <div class="traits-grid">
    <div class="trait-card" style="--trait-color: #C4A265">
      <div class="trait-header">
        <h3>Warm</h3>
        <span class="color-bias">Amber</span>
      </div>
      <p class="trait-description">Like a trusted friend, not a cold machine</p>

      <div class="trait-specs">
        <div class="spec-row">
          <span class="label">Animation</span>
          <span>Gentle, 1.2× timing</span>
        </div>
        <div class="spec-row">
          <span class="label">Haptic</span>
          <span>ferniBreath</span>
        </div>
        <div class="spec-row">
          <span class="label">Sonic</span>
          <span>Felt piano</span>
        </div>
        <div class="spec-row">
          <span class="label">Voice</span>
          <span>Soft-spoken</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="trait-patterns">
        <span class="pattern good">Inviting</span>
        <span class="pattern good">Encouraging</span>
        <span class="pattern good">Supportive</span>
      </div>
      <div class="trait-avoids">
        <span class="avoid">Cold</span>
        <span class="avoid">Clinical</span>
        <span class="avoid">Distant</span>
